name: Empty Playground Magazine - Issue 6
description:
This issue features 64 colour pages of Interviews, Reviews, News, Articles and loads of new features. There’s also a special page which includes a password which you will be able to use on a secret part of this website to download 10 great songs from bands featured in the issue!

	There are interviews with bands such as Job For A Cowboy, The Black Dahlia Murder, Alexisonfire, The Red Chord, Amenti aswell as music photographer Cindy Frey! There are also more new, exciting features and sections on some of the hottest new metal bands around.

name: Empty Playground Magazine - Issue 5
description: This issue saw us step it up a notch, with full colour and a glossy finish along with a great cover CD. Included in this issue were Misery Signals, Lordi, Everytime I Die, Killswitch Engage, Mastodon, Slayer and oh so much more! Order your now as there’s only a very limited number of these left.
